{"symbol": "NIPBL", "uniprot": "Q6KC79", "protein_name": "Nipped-B-like protein", "length": 2804, "function": "Plays an important role in the loading of the cohesin complex on to DNA. Forms a heterodimeric complex (also known as cohesin loading complex) with MAU2/SCC4 which mediates the loading of the cohesin complex onto chromatin (PubMed:22628566, PubMed:28914604). Plays a role in cohesin loading at sites of DNA damage. Its recruitment to double-strand breaks (DSBs) sites occurs in a CBX3-, RNF8- and RNF168-dependent manner whereas its recruitment to UV irradiation-induced DNA damage sites occurs in a ATM-, ATR-, RNF8- and RNF168-dependent manner (PubMed:28167679). Along with ZNF609, promotes cortical neuron migration during brain development by regulating the transcription of crucial genes in this process. Preferentially binds promoters containing paused RNA polymerase II. Up-regulates the expression of SEMA3A, NRP1, PLXND1 and GABBR2 genes, among others (By similarity)", "ensembl_gene": "ENSG00000164190", "scores": {"selectivity": 0.3458, "protein_drug": 0.228, "rna_drug": 0.316}, "flags": {"surface": false, "enzyme": false, "mod_aso": true, "mod_sirna": false}, "details": {"nominated_modality": "ASO", "winning_axis": "RNA", "quadrant": "RNA-preferred", "best_route": "small molecule", "sm_score": "0.259", "sirna_score": "0.118", "aso_score": "0.223"}, "modality": "ASO", "structure": "data/structures/NIPBL.pdb", "pockets": [{"rank": 1, "druggability": 0.451, "volume": 378.4, "residues": [82, 83, 84, 85, 86, 87, 88, 92, 97, 100, 101, 104, 108]}, {"rank": 2, "druggability": 0.044, "volume": 447.9, "residues": [45, 48, 49, 52, 53, 56]}, {"rank": 3, "druggability": 0.035, "volume": 369.8, "residues": [1042, 1043, 1045, 1048, 1049, 1071, 1074, 1075, 1078]}], "links": [{"key": "uniprot", "label": "UniProt", "url": "https://www.uniprot.org/uniprotkb/Q6KC79"}, {"key": "alphafold", "label": "AlphaFold", "url": "https://alphafold.ebi.ac.uk/entry/Q6KC79"}, {"key": "opentargets", "label": "Open Targets", "url": "https://platform.opentargets.org/target/ENSG00000164190"}, {"key": "genecards", "label": "GeneCards", "url": "https://www.genecards.org/cgi-bin/carddisp.pl?gene=NIPBL"}, {"key": "ensembl", "label": "Ensembl", "url": "https://www.ensembl.org/Homo_sapiens/Gene/Summary?g=ENSG00000164190"}, {"key": "pdb", "label": "RCSB PDB", "url": "https://www.rcsb.org/search?q=NIPBL"}, {"key": "string", "label": "STRING", "url": "https://string-db.org/cgi/network?identifiers=NIPBL&species=9606"}, {"key": "pubmed", "label": "PubMed", "url": "https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/?term=NIPBL+AND+T+cell"}], "rna": {"transcript": "ENST00000282516", "mrna_len": 10425, "sites": [{"pos": 566, "start": 556, "end": 577, "modality": "ASO", "score": 0.285, "seq": "TGAACCAGCTGCCTCTTCCATC"}, {"pos": 588, "start": 578, "end": 599, "modality": "ASO", "score": 0.092, "seq": "TCCTTTACCTGCTACAACTACA"}, {"pos": 898, "start": 888, "end": 909, "modality": "ASO", "score": 0.289, "seq": "CACAGTAGTCCTGCATCTTCCA"}, {"pos": 924, "start": 914, "end": 935, "modality": "ASO", "score": 0.157, "seq": "TCAACAAACCACTATCTCACAT"}, {"pos": 1047, "start": 1037, "end": 1058, "modality": "ASO", "score": 0.297, "seq": "TGCAGGATACATGCCATATTCC"}, {"pos": 1069, "start": 1059, "end": 1080, "modality": "ASO", "score": 0.276, "seq": "CATCCTTCAAGTTACACAACAC"}, {"pos": 1368, "start": 1358, "end": 1379, "modality": "ASO", "score": 0.29, "seq": "CTCAAGACCACCTTTAATCCTA"}, {"pos": 1390, "start": 1380, "end": 1401, "modality": "ASO", "score": 0.153, "seq": "CAATCTCAGTCTCTACCTTGTT"}, {"pos": 1503, "start": 1493, "end": 1514, "modality": "ASO", "score": 0.241, "seq": "AAAAGAGCAGAGTGAGAAAGCG"}, {"pos": 1668, "start": 1658, "end": 1679, "modality": "ASO", "score": 0.268, "seq": "TCCTTTTAATGTGCAGTACCCA"}, {"pos": 1702, "start": 1692, "end": 1713, "modality": "ASO", "score": 0.062, "seq": "AAAACACCCATTACTCCACAAG"}, {"pos": 1767, "start": 1757, "end": 1778, "modality": "ASO", "score": 0.277, "seq": "AGAACAAACA